                <head>No. 423<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>For an extract of notes of a conversation on May 14 between the Secretary and
                    Allen Dulles concerning Ambassador Donovan’s proposal for a United States
                    airbase in Thailand and the possibility of a security treaty with Thailand, see
                        <ref target="frus1952-54v12p1#pg_485">Part 1, page 485</ref>.</p>
